This router may have only been sold under other names. :It is, however, noted as a BR-6428n in the FCC docs.
The FCC test report has the following under the multiple listing table.. *''[[Edimax]]'' GR-428N *[[Airlink101 AR675W]] *''SK Broadband'' MW-2060AP *''CANYON'' CNP-WF514N3 *''Getnet'' GR-724W
